586
00:45:22,027 --> 00:45:24,200
'Cause I'm about
to give away his job.

587
00:45:24,590 --> 00:45:27,368
But this one time Lafayette
went to Marthaville for the night.

588
00:45:27,493 --> 00:45:30,462
