593
00:45:52,599 --> 00:45:54,403
I hope you're right about that,

594
00:45:54,528 --> 00:45:55,350
Terry.

595
00:45:57,266 --> 00:45:59,754
Your hair's like a sunset
after a bomb went off.

596
